This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech recognition and natural language processing. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with audio data. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses deep learning models and optimization techniques. It could also be classified under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it deals with production systems and deployment. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it discusses strategies to reduce bias in machine learning models.
